{"tid":22222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被批不懂兩岸　幕僚：川普很清楚","createTime":"2016-12-04T10:17:17.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-05T12:13:48.000Z","uid":2339,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a865b61259d540c13ec27b4c50a603af40fd33b","tid":22222,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T10:17:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20161204/1003974/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20161204%2F1003974%2F&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=cfcbe22c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20161204/1003974/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統當選人川普與總統蔡英文通電話，創美台斷交37年來首次領導人直接對話。政治學者指，美方因與中共簽署3個《公報》，「認知」到海峽兩岸同屬一個中國，美國總統長期以來會避免與台灣的領導人直接通話。<br />\n<br />\n美國《大西洋》月刊點出，川普此舉顯露出美方長期遵守的一些外交準則非常怪誕（weird），分析美、中、台三方透過維持兩岸同屬一個中國的假象（fiction），藉此交往。這個假象不只是美國的「一個中國」政策所維持，也獲兩岸的「九二共識」支持，「台北與北京承認只有一個中國，但誰是合法政府各說各話。」<br />\n<br />\n川普發言人康薇否認川普因不懂兩岸局勢而和蔡總統通話，她說川普「很清楚美國向來的政策。」川普先前很少提及對台政策，僅在選舉造勢時提及台灣也在搶走美國人的工作，也曾批美國不賣F-16 C/D給台灣。但他的智囊有非常友台的人物。<br />\n<br />\n川普經濟幕僚，加州大學爾灣分校商學院的教授納瓦羅（Peter Navarro）曾力陳美國不能放任中國「霸凌」台灣，美國不該虧待台灣。<br />\n<br />\n共和黨議員也紛紛讚揚川普，眾議員外交委員會亞太小組主席邵建隆（Matt Salmon）說，對於川普向全球展現支持民主價值，給予掌聲。參議員柯頓（Tom Cotton）讚許這是對「華人土地上唯一民主國度」的再次認可。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n侵侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb7ea5cf12759a06b089f671c921059c2452e52f","tid":22222,"uid":25350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T10:26:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da90e8806a5fd88821d66d41e52c8c2348581899","tid":22222,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:32:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2e893254463bb700880792754be251e990b5d7","tid":22222,"uid":30743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:38:21.000Z","msg":"中國邏輯：這是中國內政，不容許別國干預<br />\n<br />\n但打個電話都玻璃心，都要理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b286703d4b9a37a027786316ef5b1971c521b9","tid":22222,"uid":13614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:40:23.000Z","msg":"川普很清楚台獨邊個責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2050547474c7afa5c392b37b11fa0cf2982863b6","tid":22222,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:41:36.000Z","msg":"諗起之前啲支那人打晒j<br />\n話特朗普親中，台灣收皮就想笑"},{"pid":"d8900d1b23f80e30b5bd75414eff6920dbf48200","tid":22222,"uid":30743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:45:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起之前啲支那人打晒j<br />\n話特朗普親中，台灣收皮就想笑</blockquote><br />\n吳彥祖投 hiliary 俾大陸仔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2e71a05bbc2e334371d0b16b971bb581fe9052f","tid":22222,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:48:32.000Z","msg":"特朗普對華政策點? 行動答x左你支那國啦<br />\n<br />\n1.和第一個見面的領導人是 安倍<br />\n2.公開話無收過支那電話<br />\n3.接蔡英文電話<br />\n4.準備安排台灣官員團隊見面<br />\n<br />\n藍絲and支那傳媒,唔洗日日再自己呃自己<br />\n做定亡國準備啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52cc3595a572624d5c68e564d60138d5a6eb2125","tid":22222,"uid":15205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:53:08.000Z","msg":"人地而家有話唔支持一個中國咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係侵支持台灣才是中國正宗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0d9157ce859a8cc67bc4b55c94a72e387c165f","tid":22222,"uid